{"pageContext":{"group":[{"node":{"id":"8b7ea332-0674-5442-a613-b65e91fe9ff2","slug":"creative-development-inspiration-10","template":"","format":"standard","title":"Creative and Development Inspiration 10","date":"2018-01-01T09:48:56.000Z","excerpt":"<p>Starting this year as I plan to go on, with a good old list. This time I have brought together 6 articles that look across the year to help you develop your skill set, as well as a glance back at the past year. &nbsp; 2017 Web Design Trends The list would&#8217;nt be complete without [&hellip;]</p>\n","featured_media":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.829268292682927,"src":"/static/8c052da0762040d40b0a9aa2e2f9e7ac/3b7c4/Froala.jpg","srcSet":"/static/8c052da0762040d40b0a9aa2e2f9e7ac/03841/Froala.jpg 250w,\n/static/8c052da0762040d40b0a9aa2e2f9e7ac/26396/Froala.jpg 500w,\n/static/8c052da0762040d40b0a9aa2e2f9e7ac/3b7c4/Froala.jpg 750w","sizes":"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px"}}},"title":"Froala","alt_text":"Froala Design Blocks"},"categories":[{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"Creative"},{"name":"Design"},{"name":"General Coding"},{"name":"Inspiration"}],"tags":[{"name":"Bootstrap 4"},{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"Design"},{"name":"Inspiration"},{"name":"Interfaces"},{"name":"JS"},{"name":"predictions"},{"name":"Snippets"},{"name":"Trends"}]}},{"node":{"id":"6a1f5b99-43f8-504d-a7b9-d131ac3b9a85","slug":"creative-development-inspiration-9","template":"","format":"standard","title":"Creative and Development Inspiration 9","date":"2017-12-18T12:00:52.000Z","excerpt":"<p>Because next week is Christmas (and I won&#8217;t be creating a list, family and all that) I have pulled together a longer selection than usual. This week there have been some really great pieces of code coming to the surface, as well as some great graphic design inspiration. &nbsp; DesignClever I&#8217;ll kick off with DesignClever. [&hellip;]</p>\n","featured_media":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.829268292682927,"src":"/static/e2fc2ef77b63f29c80ea5fbdae44bb87/3b7c4/purple-1.jpg","srcSet":"/static/e2fc2ef77b63f29c80ea5fbdae44bb87/03841/purple-1.jpg 250w,\n/static/e2fc2ef77b63f29c80ea5fbdae44bb87/26396/purple-1.jpg 500w,\n/static/e2fc2ef77b63f29c80ea5fbdae44bb87/3b7c4/purple-1.jpg 750w","sizes":"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px"}}},"title":"purple (1)","alt_text":"Purple is 2018 colour"},"categories":[{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"Creative"},{"name":"Design"},{"name":"General Coding"},{"name":"Inspiration"}],"tags":[{"name":"Animated"},{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"CSS"},{"name":"Design"},{"name":"Features"},{"name":"Highlights"},{"name":"Inspiration"},{"name":"JS"},{"name":"Menu"},{"name":"Purple"},{"name":"Snippets"},{"name":"Visualiser"}]}},{"node":{"id":"a76bd53b-0a9c-5c13-ab12-baa8568a49f8","slug":"creative-development-inspiration-8","template":"","format":"standard","title":"Creative and Development Inspiration 8","date":"2017-12-11T10:04:52.000Z","excerpt":"<p>This week I have pulled together 6 pieces from across the design interwebs to showcase some of the best articles, code snippets and a little bit of inspiration to get you started. &nbsp; User Experience Matters to Marketing User Experience (UX) can effect your marketing, if users view it positively. This post looks at the [&hellip;]</p>\n","featured_media":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.829268292682927,"src":"/static/f4ecb7ae4c39955906bdb3d7d355ef0c/3b7c4/Code-Drops-Animated-SVG.jpg","srcSet":"/static/f4ecb7ae4c39955906bdb3d7d355ef0c/03841/Code-Drops-Animated-SVG.jpg 250w,\n/static/f4ecb7ae4c39955906bdb3d7d355ef0c/26396/Code-Drops-Animated-SVG.jpg 500w,\n/static/f4ecb7ae4c39955906bdb3d7d355ef0c/3b7c4/Code-Drops-Animated-SVG.jpg 750w","sizes":"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px"}}},"title":"Code-Drops-Animated-SVG","alt_text":"Animated SVG Strokes"},"categories":[{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"Creative"},{"name":"General Coding"},{"name":"Ramblings"}],"tags":[{"name":"Animated"},{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"CSS"},{"name":"Design"},{"name":"Inspiration"},{"name":"JS"},{"name":"Snippets"}]}},{"node":{"id":"2af9bf47-85fb-5e12-a754-1b944dec8931","slug":"creative-development-inspiration-7","template":"","format":"standard","title":"Creative and Development Inspiration 7","date":"2017-12-04T13:36:11.000Z","excerpt":"<p>This week I have brought together 6 links that cover design, code and process. Some great pieces of inspiration as well as some hopefully useful snippets to enhance your work. &nbsp; Website Design Example A brief look at the new website for Heydays from Oslo. Its nice. Its simple. I like it. Also, its pretty [&hellip;]</p>\n","featured_media":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.829268292682927,"src":"/static/f04cc3cf9e0edbc54fb735d491ca8777/3b7c4/Heydays-new-website.jpg","srcSet":"/static/f04cc3cf9e0edbc54fb735d491ca8777/03841/Heydays-new-website.jpg 250w,\n/static/f04cc3cf9e0edbc54fb735d491ca8777/26396/Heydays-new-website.jpg 500w,\n/static/f04cc3cf9e0edbc54fb735d491ca8777/3b7c4/Heydays-new-website.jpg 750w","sizes":"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px"}}},"title":"Heydays new website","alt_text":"Heydays new website"},"categories":[{"name":"Branding"},{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"Creative"},{"name":"Design"},{"name":"Inspiration"},{"name":"UX"}],"tags":[{"name":"CSS"},{"name":"Design"},{"name":"Design System"},{"name":"Inspiration"},{"name":"JS"},{"name":"Photoshop"},{"name":"Snippets"},{"name":"Trends"},{"name":"UX"}]}},{"node":{"id":"8e4e033b-aaf4-5e24-867a-6cd018f1c54e","slug":"creative-development-inspiration-6","template":"","format":"standard","title":"Creative and Development Inspiration 6","date":"2017-11-28T10:15:54.000Z","excerpt":"<p>This weeks list is more design focused, with a story telling script thrown in for good measure. As most design/dev sites are shouting about Cyber Monday deals, I wanted to keep this on the same track as we started. I hope you enjoy. &nbsp; Designercize Needing to flex your design muscles? A little down time [&hellip;]</p>\n","featured_media":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.829268292682927,"src":"/static/bbd94dde785a45276e4372b40eb76c7b/3b7c4/YELLOW.jpg","srcSet":"/static/bbd94dde785a45276e4372b40eb76c7b/03841/YELLOW.jpg 250w,\n/static/bbd94dde785a45276e4372b40eb76c7b/26396/YELLOW.jpg 500w,\n/static/bbd94dde785a45276e4372b40eb76c7b/3b7c4/YELLOW.jpg 750w","sizes":"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px"}}},"title":"YELLOW","alt_text":"An example of yellow websites"},"categories":[{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"Creative"},{"name":"General Coding"},{"name":"Ramblings"}],"tags":[{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"Design"},{"name":"Inspiration"},{"name":"JS"},{"name":"Storytelling"},{"name":"Type"},{"name":"Yellow"}]}},{"node":{"id":"33a09e38-75d8-5d09-b045-a1b22a1e0356","slug":"creative-and-development-inspiration-5-feature-highlights","template":"","format":"standard","title":"Creative and Development Inspiration 5: Feature Highlights","date":"2017-11-20T13:19:07.000Z","excerpt":"<p>Finding ways to display hidden information for users can be tough. The number of times brochure websites have required some level of user engagement and I have had to scour the web for examples such as these. I thought I should share. &nbsp; Project Feature Highlights By adding tooltips into div elements they can be positioned anywhere [&hellip;]</p>\n","featured_media":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.9569471624266144,"src":"/static/6d098269bafc3ddbfa350ee8cd3d22ff/1a92f/hover-tooltip.jpg","srcSet":"/static/6d098269bafc3ddbfa350ee8cd3d22ff/788f9/hover-tooltip.jpg 250w,\n/static/6d098269bafc3ddbfa350ee8cd3d22ff/06f71/hover-tooltip.jpg 500w,\n/static/6d098269bafc3ddbfa350ee8cd3d22ff/1a92f/hover-tooltip.jpg 1000w","sizes":"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px"}}},"title":"Hover Tooltip Header","alt_text":"Animated button tooltips"},"categories":[{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"Creative"},{"name":"General Coding"}],"tags":[{"name":"Animated"},{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"CSS"},{"name":"Design"},{"name":"Features"},{"name":"Highlights"},{"name":"Hover"},{"name":"JS"},{"name":"Mouseover"},{"name":"Snippets"},{"name":"Teaching"},{"name":"Tooltips"}]}},{"node":{"id":"c80c112a-50b5-52bc-9ba6-380b4c3a32eb","slug":"creative-and-development-inspiration-4-hidden-menus","template":"","format":"standard","title":"Creative and Development Inspiration 4: Hidden Menus","date":"2017-11-13T10:05:25.000Z","excerpt":"<p>Today&#8217;s post is focusing on code snippets for hidden menus. These could be used on both mobile and large devices. Although they are not particularly attractive menus, I am focusing more on the usability and style. The purpose is to help inspire. &nbsp; Simple multilevel menu This menu is a code snippet from Cody House. [&hellip;]</p>\n","featured_media":{"localFile":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.829268292682927,"src":"/static/5eccdd0964125c62a43ad3f876db702c/3b7c4/Google-Material-Mobile-Menus.jpg","srcSet":"/static/5eccdd0964125c62a43ad3f876db702c/03841/Google-Material-Mobile-Menus.jpg 250w,\n/static/5eccdd0964125c62a43ad3f876db702c/26396/Google-Material-Mobile-Menus.jpg 500w,\n/static/5eccdd0964125c62a43ad3f876db702c/3b7c4/Google-Material-Mobile-Menus.jpg 750w","sizes":"(max-width: 750px) 100vw, 750px"}}},"title":"Google Material Mobile Menus","alt_text":"Google Material Mobile Menus"},"categories":[{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"Creative"},{"name":"General Coding"}],"tags":[{"name":"Coding"},{"name":"CSS"},{"name":"Design"},{"name":"Google"},{"name":"Hover"},{"name":"JS"},{"name":"Material"},{"name":"Menu"},{"name":"Mouseover"}]}},{"node":{"id":"bc6d2f2c-d038-58bf-90f1-e5845da96499","slug":"creative-and-development-inspiration-3-hover-effects","template":"","format":"s